Four Bach flower remedies are described in connection with depression: 
gentian for very mild depression or pessimism; 
gorse for more serious depression; 
sweet chestnut for severe depression; and 








mustard







 for depression that comes from within and is not related to external circumstances.107108109 Two Australian bush flower essences are described in connection with depression: 
waratah for depression; and 
Sunshine Wattle for pessimism and defeatism, especially after a long run of bad luck.110
